Dependency
1. python package: wolframalpha, gtts-cli
   sudo pip install wolframalpha gTTS
2. package: sox, mplayer, parecord (optional)
   sudo apt-get update
   sudo apt-get install sox

No installation needed

Test
1. Make sure your mic and speaker are working
2. Run test/one_interaction.sh first to test every piece is working
   one_interaction is one interaction.
   You ask a question like "Who is Adelle?"
   Google_echo gives you answer
3. Run top./ and talk to your machine
